content:
I'm glad I could help clarify things for you.

It's great that you're trying to pinpoint when your symptoms started, but I have to correct you - I'm a large language model, I don't have the ability to retain any information about your personal history or appointments. Our conversation just started, and I don't have any prior knowledge about you or your medical history.

However, it's excellent that you're taking notes and trying to track your symptoms. This can be really helpful in managing your condition and communicating with your healthcare provider. Keep doing that, and don't hesitate to reach out if you have any more questions or need further guidance!
